creator: Brandão Design
descriptionHtml:
With the FUTSHARE app it is easier to join the crowd to cheer for your team.

An app developed for amateur teams to share their soccer, amateur games or society games on social networks.

Create custom banners to publicize the games and share with your friends

CONFRONTATIONS:
Add the shields of your team and your opponent, inform the location of the event date and post directly on your team's profile.

SCOREBOARD:
Share the result of your games celebrate with your fans.

YOUR TEAM SHIELD:
Select one of the Team's Shields or send your team's shield.

ADVERSARY SHIELD:
Select one of your opponent's shields or send your opponent's shield.

CUSTOM THEMES:
Choose one of the Background Theme or send one through your photo gallery.

FLOATING ITEMS:
Drag items to best fit your custom layout.

MAIN SOCIAL NETWORKS:
Share on Instagram, Facebook or Whatsapp.
descriptionShort: Share your team's games on social media
